// !Instalation step

// 1. index.ts
// 2. terminal with -> tsc .\index.ts
// 3. tsc --init
// 4. npm init -y 
// 4. pakage.json file with push sripts into ->  "start": "nodemon index.js",
// 5. npm i -D nodemon
// 6. npm i ts-node-dev --save-dev -> auto tsc compailer ts to js convert
// 7. we use pakage.json file with push sripts into , replace with "nodemon index.js" -> "ts-node-dev --respawn --transpile-only index.ts"